content: madjin: Led a major documentation overhaul with 8 merged PRs totaling over +171k/-133k lines, primarily focused on creating and updating the community section (#745, #1111, #1114, #1211). Created 10 issues related to documentation improvements and feature ideas, all of which were closed during the month. Contributed significantly to JSDoc documentation efforts with PRs #1548 and #1549, while maintaining an active review presence with 9 code reviews and 19 comments across issues and PRs. Activity pattern shows focused work on documentation days, with substantial contributions spread across approximately 12 days of the month.
